this is a small api that serves json formatted data for an app called aBattleTour. aBattletour is an Aurelia app also on this github account.



START SERVER

node server


MONGO

    start mongo in c9
    - >>mongod --bind_ip=$IP --dbpath=data --nojournal
    
    
    after unclean shutdown
    - delete mongo.lock
    - >>mongod --repair